<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued November 28 at 8:48PM MST until November 29 at 9:00AM MST by NWS GrandJunction</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM MST
TUESDAY...
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of up to 2
inches.
* WHERE...Grand Valley.
* WHEN...Until 9 AM MST Tuesday.
* IMPACTS...Icy to snow packed roadways will create hazardous
driving conditions. A detailed map of the snowfall can be
found at: www.weather.gov/gjt/winter.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.
The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.</instruction>
